title: Roger Goodell, Rookies, Drew Brees, Dabo Swinney
itunes:title: Roger Goodell, Rookies, Drew Brees, Dabo Swinney
description:
Colin discusses why he believes Roger Goodell made the right choice by siding with the players, why he's for starting rookie QBs, his thoughts on the Drew Brees backlash, and why he feels Dabo Swinney made a mistake. Guests include Chris Broussard, Warren Moon, Justin Gaethje, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
